---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Donut Cove Consulting - Software Solutions That Save Time" 
	description="Structural software solutions for business operations. We build internal tools, custom applications, and automated workflows."
>
	<!-- Hero Section with Organic Blobs -->
	<section class="relative py-32 md:py-48 overflow-hidden">
		<!-- Organic Background Blobs -->
		<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
			<div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse"></div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-indigo/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="max-w-4xl relative z-10">
			<h1 class="font-display font-black text-6xl md:text-8xl tracking-tight leading-[0.95] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-8 drop-shadow-sm">
				Software<br />
				Solutions<br />
				<span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">That Save Time.</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
				We eliminate manual processes and build resilient software infrastructure. 
				Efficiency is not a luxury; it is a structural necessity.
			</p>
			
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-12">
				<a href="/contact" class="bg-indigo text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-indigo-dark hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-indigo/20">
					Start Project
				</a>
				<a href="/case-studies" class="bg-white dark:bg-white/10 border-2 border-coral/30 text-ink dark:text-ink-dark px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:border-coral hover:bg-coral/5 transition-all duration-300">
					See Our Results
				</a>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Integration Logos Strip -->
			<div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-ink/10 dark:border-ink-dark/10 w-full">
				<p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-ink/40 mb-4">We Integrate With</p>
				<div class="overflow-hidden w-full">
					<div class="flex gap-8 text-ink/50 font-display text-xl font-bold grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500 integration-carousel">
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Stripe</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">QuickBooks</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Shopify</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Slack</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Excel</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Salesforce</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">HubSpot</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Zapier</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Airtable</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Notion</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Google Workspace</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Microsoft 365</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">AWS</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Azure</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">PostgreSQL</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">MongoDB</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">GitHub</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Jira</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Asana</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Stripe</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">QuickBooks</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Shopify</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Slack</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Excel</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Salesforce</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">HubSpot</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Zapier</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Airtable</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Notion</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Google Workspace</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Microsoft 365</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">AWS</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Azure</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">PostgreSQL</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">MongoDB</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">GitHub</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Jira</span>
						<span class="whitespace-nowrap">Asana</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Pain Section: Where are you losing money? -->
	<section class="py-24 relative">
		<div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-16 shadow-xl shadow-indigo/5 border border-indigo/10">
			<h2 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl mb-16 text-center text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
				Where are you <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">losing money?</span>
			</h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
				<div class="space-y-4 text-center group">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-coral-light/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">üìâ</div>
					<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Manual Entry Hell</h3>
					<p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
						Copy-pasting between Excel and your CRM? It's slow, error-prone, and costing you hours every week.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="space-y-4 text-center group">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-indigo/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">üï∏Ô∏è</div>
					<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Broken Workflows</h3>
					<p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
						Chasing emails for approvals? Losing track of inventory? We build systems that flow automatically.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="space-y-4 text-center group">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-sunflower/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">üê¢</div>
					<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Legacy Slowdowns</h3>
					<p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
						Waiting for old software to load? We modernize legacy tools into fast, web-based platforms.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Services Grid -->
	<section class="py-24">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-4">
			<h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-tight leading-[0.95] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
				Core<br />
				<span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Services</span>
			</h2>
			<a href="/services" class="hidden md:inline-block font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo font-bold hover:text-indigo-dark transition-colors">
				View All ‚Üí
			</a>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
			<!-- Service 1 -->
			<div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-coral/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-coral/20 group">
				<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl mb-4 group-hover:text-coral-vibrant transition-colors">Internal Tools</h3>
				<p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
					Custom dashboards, inventory systems, and admin panels. We replace spreadsheets with robust databases.
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-3 font-medium text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-coral"></span> Data Entry Automation</li>
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-coral"></span> Legacy Modernization</li>
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-coral"></span> React / Node.js</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Service 2 -->
			<div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-10 rounded-[2rem] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-indigo/20 group">
				<h3 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl mb-4 group-hover:text-indigo transition-colors">Custom Applications</h3>
				<p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
					Tailored software built for your specific business logic. Scalable, secure, and maintainable.
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-3 font-medium text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo"></span> Web Platforms</li>
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo"></span> API Integration</li>
					<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo"></span> SaaS Products</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

        <!-- Case Study Teaser -->
        <div class="mt-12 p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo to-indigo-dark rounded-[2rem] text-white shadow-xl shadow-indigo/20 relative overflow-hidden group">
			<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start md:items-center justify-between relative z-10">
                <div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60">Featured Case Study</span>
                    <h4 class="font-display font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight leading-[0.95] mt-2">Logistics<br /><span class="italic">Automation</span></h4>
                    <p class="text-white/80 mt-2 text-lg">Saved 20h/week by replacing Excel with Node.js.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/case-studies" class="bg-white text-indigo font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-coral-light hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 shadow-lg">Read Case Study</a>
            </div>
        </div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA -->
	<section class="py-32 text-center">
		<h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-8 tracking-tighter text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
			Ready to <span class="text-indigo italic">build?</span>
		</h2>
		<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-coral-vibrant text-white px-12 py-6 rounded-full font-bold text-2xl hover:bg-coral hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl shadow-coral/30">
			Let's Talk
		</a>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.integration-carousel {
		animation: scroll 60s linear infinite;
		width: fit-content;
	}
	
	@keyframes scroll {
		0% {
			transform: translateX(0);
		}
		100% {
			transform: translateX(-50%);
		}
	}
	
	.integration-carousel:hover {
		animation-play-state: paused;
	}
</style>
